ar and simmer for <b>15 min\/212°F\/\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Transfer into bowls and garnish with fresh Thai chilies and holy basil to serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["When using lemongrass: trim off the root and the woody stems and only use the soft white part of the grass.","Depending on the type of mushrooms you use, you may need to remove the stems if they are tough.","To make slicing the beef easier, freeze beef up to one hour prior to using."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h","4 portions"]}